<p><code><pre>gcc main.c
</pre></code></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The code should compile without any issues and produce the executable program 'a.out'. &nbsp;You can run this program with this command:</p>

<p><code><pre>./a.out
</pre></code></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Note that code does not represent a <em>fast</em> implementation of the regular expression (in fact it's one of the slowest implementations possible). &nbsp;The goal here is to produce a program that is very short and easy to understand for educational purposes rather than to produce one that is fast and complicated.</p>

